Class QualitySummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • toolkit.domain.QualitySummary

  • public class QualitySummary
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by James Euesden on 07/04/2016. Holds the results of each quality inspection result to be provided to the View from the Controller.
